{"tid":1931842,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"狗真係改不了吃屎","createTime":"2020-03-18T11:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T17:03:13.000Z","uid":147789,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb94ff028f680f9be65901aa68e695e6694ef18","tid":1931842,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:09:35.000Z","msg":"晚晚半夜都出廳屙屎食清光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔識奶返乾淨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朝朝起身個狗籠得返啲屎跡<br />\n<br />\n佢半夜屙 我又無理由朝早先鬧佢<br />\n佢以為我無啦啦發爛渣點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係半夜瞓緊覺我又唔知佢幾時急屎<br />\n試過等到3點都唔屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以點教佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人感受都我嘅無奈啊啊啊！！<br />\n我唔想隻狗攞個食完屎嘅死人口奶我個嘴啊啊啊啊啊！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279414d48c3089bf8ab0f8eccfe484247c0b5222","tid":1931842,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:33:54.000Z","msg":"無人隻狗會屙屎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d6b536195b5d62f3d1fca3b56319064e3495b19","tid":1931842,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T11:37:28.000Z","msg":"同人食鼻屎一樣，好難戒得甩"},{"pid":"cc3840f6e82ba42aece7cd1f784c7e99e637f284","tid":1931842,"uid":353409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"我男朋友隻狗都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重要唔食狗糧 偷偷地食矖啲屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2c85ff7781d246ee885af525c1946f8009d664","tid":1931842,"uid":88471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:01:25.000Z","msg":"試吓轉糧"},{"pid":"02ba4dea6bb9337cf038c3fdab35d992c868b3cb","tid":1931842,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f2c85ff7781d246ee885af525c1946f8009d664","tid":1931842,"uid":88471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T14:01:25.000Z","msg":"試吓轉糧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T17:03:13.000Z","msg":"老母今日先買咗包一樣嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有排先試到新糧"}]}